{"id":233,"parent_id":224,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":233,"title":"Hebrews 9","subtitle":"","short_title":"Heb.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 9"],[".studySummary",["i","The Mosaic ordinances prefigured Christ’s ministry—Christ is the Mediator of the new covenant."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.1","order":"03.21.009.23999"},["b","1"],"Then verily the first",["i",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"covenant"]],"had also",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"ordinances"],"of divine",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"service"],", and a worldly sanctuary."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.2","order":"03.21.009.24000"},["b","2"],"For there was a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"tabernacle"],"made; the first, wherein",["i","was"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"candlestick"],", and the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"table"],", and the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_2d"},"shewbread"],"; which is called the sanctuary."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.3","order":"03.21.009.24001"},["b","3"],"And after the second",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"veil"],", the tabernacle which is called the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"Holiest"],"of all;"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.4","order":"03.21.009.24002"},["b","4"],"Which had the golden censer, and the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"ark"],"of the covenant overlaid round about with gold, wherein",["i","was"],"the golden",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"pot"],"that had manna, and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"Aaron’s"],"rod that budded, and the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_4d"},"tables"],"of the covenant;"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.5","order":"03.21.009.24003"},["b","5"],"And over it the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"cherubims"],"of glory shadowing the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"mercyseat"],"; of which we cannot now speak particularly."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.6","order":"03.21.009.24004"},["b","6"],"Now when these things were thus",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"ordained"],", the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"priests"],"went always into the first tabernacle, accomplishing the service",["i","of God."]],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.7","order":"03.21.009.24005"},["b","7"],"But into the second",["i","went"],"the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"high priest"],"alone",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"once"],"every year, not without blood, which he offered for himself, and",["i","for"],"the errors of the people:"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.8","order":"03.21.009.24006"},["b","8"],"The Holy Ghost this signifying, that the way into the holiest of all was not yet made manifest, while as the first tabernacle was yet standing:"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.9","order":"03.21.009.24007"},["b","9"],"Which",["i","was"],"a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"figure"],"for the time then present, in which were offered both gifts and sacrifices, that could not make him that did the service",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"perfect"],", as pertaining to the conscience;"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.10","order":"03.21.009.24008"},["b","10"],["i","Which stood"],"only in meats and drinks, and divers",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"washings"],", and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"carnal"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"ordinances"],",",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_10d"},"imposed"],["i","on them"],"until the time of reformation."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.11","order":"03.21.009.24009"},["b","11"],"But Christ being come an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"high priest"],"of good things to come, by a greater and more perfect",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"tabernacle"],", not made with hands, that is to say, not of this building;"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.12","order":"03.21.009.24010"},["b","12"],"Neither by the blood of goats and calves, but by his own",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"blood"],"he entered in once into the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"holy place"],", having obtained eternal",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"redemption"],["i","for us."]],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.13","order":"03.21.009.24011"},["b","13"],"For if the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"blood"],"of bulls and of goats, and the ashes of an heifer sprinkling the unclean, sanctifieth to the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"purifying"],"of the flesh:"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.14","order":"03.21.009.24012"},["b","14"],"How much more shall the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"blood"],"of Christ, who through the eternal Spirit offered himself",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"without"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"spot"],"to God,",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_14d"},"purge"],"your",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_14e"},"conscience"],"from dead works to serve the living God?"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.15","order":"03.21.009.24013"},["b","15"],"And for this cause he is the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"mediator"],"of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"new"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"testament"],", that by means of",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_15d"},"death"],", for the redemption of the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_15e"},"transgressions"],["i","that were"],"under the first",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_15f"},"testament"],", they which are called might receive the",["sup","g"],["a",{"href":"fn_15g"},"promise"],"of eternal",["sup","h"],["a",{"href":"fn_15h"},"inheritance"],"."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.16","order":"03.21.009.24014"},["b","16"],"For where a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"testament"],["i","is,"],"there must also of necessity be the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"death"],"of the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_16c"},"testator"],"."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.17","order":"03.21.009.24015"},["b","17"],"For a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"testament"],["i","is"],"of force after men are dead:",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"otherwise"],"it is of no strength at all while the testator liveth."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.18","order":"03.21.009.24016"},["b","18"],"Whereupon neither the first",["i","testament"],"was dedicated without blood."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.19","order":"03.21.009.24017"},["b","19"],"For when Moses had",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"spoken"],"every precept to all the people according to the law, he took the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"blood"],"of calves and of goats, with water, and scarlet wool, and hyssop, and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_19c"},"sprinkled"],"both the book, and all the people,"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.20","order":"03.21.009.24018"},["b","20"],"Saying, This",["i","is"],"the blood of the testament which God hath enjoined unto you."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.21","order":"03.21.009.24019"},["b","21"],"Moreover he sprinkled with blood both the tabernacle, and all the vessels of the ministry."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.22","order":"03.21.009.24020"},["b","22"],"And almost all things are by the law purged with blood; and without",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"shedding"],"of blood is no",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"remission"],"."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.23","order":"03.21.009.24021"},["b","23"],["i","It was"],"therefore necessary that the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"patterns"],"of things in the heavens should be purified with these; but the heavenly things themselves with better sacrifices than these."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.24","order":"03.21.009.24022"},["b","24"],"For Christ is not entered into the holy places made with hands,",["i","which are"],"the figures of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"true"],"; but into",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"heaven"],"itself, now to appear in the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_24c"},"presence"],"of God for us:"],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.25","order":"03.21.009.24023"},["b","25"],"Nor yet that he should offer himself often, as the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"high priest"],"entereth into the holy place every year with blood of others;"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.26","order":"03.21.009.24024"},["b","26"],"For then must he often have suffered since the foundation of the world: but now once",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"in"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"end of the world"],"hath he appeared to put away sin by the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_26c"},"sacrifice"],"of himself."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.27","order":"03.21.009.24025"},["b","27"],"And as it is appointed unto men once to die, but after this the judgment:"],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.28","order":"03.21.009.24026"},["b","28"],"So Christ was once",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"offered"],"to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_28b"},"bear"],"the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_28c"},"sins"],"of many; and unto them that look for him shall he",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_28d"},"appear"],"the second time without sin unto salvation."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.1a","order":"03.21.009.24027"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/law-of-moses"},"TG Law of Moses"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.1b","order":"03.21.009.24029"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/ordinance"},"TG Ordinance"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.1c","order":"03.21.009.24031"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/service"},"TG Service"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.2a","order":"03.21.009.24033"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/26.1.1-37"},"Ex. 26:1 (1–37)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/39.33"},"39:33"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.2b","order":"03.21.009.24035"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/25.31.31-39"},"Ex. 25:31 (31–39)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/26.35"},"26:35"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.2c","order":"03.21.009.24037"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/25.23.23-29"},"Ex. 25:23 (23–29)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/24.6"},"Lev. 24:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"2d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.2d","order":"03.21.009.24039"},["b","2d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/25.30"},"Ex. 25:30"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.3a","order":"03.21.009.24041"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-types-of-in-anticipation"},"TG Jesus Christ, Types of, in Anticipation"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/veil"},"Veil"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.3b","order":"03.21.009.24043"},["b","3b"],["span.small","GR"],"Holy of holies."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.4a","order":"03.21.009.24045"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/ark-of-the-covenant"},"TG Ark of the Covenant"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.4b","order":"03.21.009.24047"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/16.33.33-34"},"Ex. 16:33 (33–34)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.4c","order":"03.21.009.24049"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/17.10"},"Num. 17:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"4d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.4d","order":"03.21.009.24051"},["b","4d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/25.16.16,20,40"},"Ex. 25:16 (16, 20, 40)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.5a","order":"03.21.009.24053"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/cherubim"},"TG Cherubim"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.5b","order":"03.21.009.24055"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/25.17"},"Ex. 25:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.6a","order":"03.21.009.24057"},["b","6a"],["span.small","GR"],"prepared, built."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.6b","order":"03.21.009.24059"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priest-aaronic-priesthood"},"TG Priest, Aaronic Priesthood"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bd/priests"},"BD Priests"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.7a","order":"03.21.009.24061"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.25"},"Heb. 9:25"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.3"},"10:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.7b","order":"03.21.009.24063"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/30.10"},"Ex. 30:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.9a","order":"03.21.009.24065"},["b","9a"],["span.small","GR"],"similitude, type, parable.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-types-of-in-anticipation"},"TG Jesus Christ, Types of, in Anticipation"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.9b","order":"03.21.009.24067"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/7.19"},"Heb. 7:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.10a","order":"03.21.009.24069"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/wash"},"TG Wash"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.10b","order":"03.21.009.24071"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/7.16"},"Heb. 7:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.10c","order":"03.21.009.24073"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/ordinance"},"TG Ordinance"],"."],["div",{"id":"10d","ur